commit 72bb61e76a11b00119cd18dc0fc7c7eeef137a01
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Sat Dec 12 16:49:19 2020 +0100

    gschem: Update German translation

commit f752c1cd21817ef7eee63fed9a56a2ad47a5792a
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Wed Dec 16 18:14:08 2020 +0100

    Regenerate PO files

commit 4b4092705d5e7181e0c6dfb4fc8fb4c0f6b13e62
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Mon Dec 14 18:19:01 2020 +0100

    gschem: Don't scroll log window unless realized
    
    gtk_text_view_scroll_to_iter doesn't check if the text view has a
    layout; if it hasn't, an assertion in gtk_text_layout_get_iter_location
    is violated, and the program aborts.  In order to avoid that, check if
    the text view is realized before trying to scroll it.

commit 359d1cf8abd3da9866d2d39f4b3ca7d9f82d8383
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Mon Dec 14 14:51:50 2020 +0100

    gschem: Fix order in which gschem is quit

