commit fe23971c333c2c86abe40ddb1c15424565ef826a
Author: Peter TB Brett <peter@peter-b.co.uk>
Date:   Mon Jan 23 11:09:48 2017 +0000

    gschem: Fix window smob lifetime issues
    
    Ensure that when a `GschemToplevel` instance has a smob created and
    cached for it, that smob is protected from garbage collection until
    the instance is destroyed.
    
    (cherry-picked from lepton-eda commit 7cd8b93)

