Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Thu Aug 8 14:46:22 2019 +0200

    gschem: Warn if current page is in inconsistent state

commit 17182c2399f9b0850adc588d7b9193c792e50277
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Thu Aug 8 14:38:54 2019 +0200

    gschem: Don't set page view page directly
    
    Switching the current page via gschem_page_view_set_page bypasses some
    user interface updates.  Use x_window_set_current_page instead.

