    gschem: Make sure to restore correct page after calling s_page_goto

commit b1e751f8aed7f0cfe0aca450bfc57372dbbd0eae
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Thu Aug 8 14:16:42 2019 +0200

    gschem: close confirmation: Use x_window_set_current_page
    
    When changing the current page for the close confirmation dialog, use
    x_window_set_current_page to update the page view accordingly.

commit 9aee62ed7dc8cbe5bb09e58edf18c32386a02eaf
Author: Roland Lutz <rlutz@hedmen.org>
Date:   Thu Aug 8 14:14:10 2019 +0200

    gschem: Restore consistent current page after s_hierarchy_* calls
    
    The hierarchy descension functions change the toplevel context's
    current page without calling x_window_set_current_page.  Restore the
    current page after calling these functions and set it properly using
    x_window_set_current_page.

