commit 79f469d9c2b235e6dbc3656952cd54a356e6fa26
Author: Igor2 <gedau@igor2.repo.hu>
Date:   Mon Sep 7 06:11:34 2015 +0000

    [ba] -Add: build a hash of net_info nodes
    [ba] -Change: move net conn check code into a common static function since most of the action is the same for del and add
    
