Date:   Thu Nov 12 17:00:08 2015 +0300

    gschem: Fix segfaults on 'Page revert'.
    
    Fixes segfaults happening when the 'Page revert' action is run after
    the page file was changed in another program.

commit 79d6da9e2dec05716570ae9b99ba65f5ddec5bbc
Author: Sergey Alyoshin <alyoshin.s@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Nov 8 13:04:42 2015 +0300

    gschem: multiattrib Value textview improvements
    
    * Move focus backward to Name from Value textview with Shift+Tab
    * Add tooltip for Value textview about adding new line and Tab
    * Allow horizontal scrollbar for Value textview to prevent dialog window to
      expand more than display size
    
    Reviewed-by: Vladimir Zhbanov <vzhbanov@gmail.com>
    
    Closes-bug: lp-1514209

commit bcae3e0cba7f62b3fdcf734a271b26cb70c97f97
Author: Sergey Stepanov <no.such.process@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Oct 1 00:58:25 2015 +0500

    change sqrt(x*x+y*y) -> hypot(x,y)
    
    this change has 3 benefits:
    * hypot() calculation is performed without undue overflow or underflow;
    * code behaviour less compiler dependent, than pow(x, 2), which (probably) may fail if x is negative;
    * code is a bit simpler, and less error prone if x or y is a complex expression.

commit 2cfa186bde319325eacf03c496b80df9dcc097e7
Author: Vladimir Zhbanov <vzhbanov@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Oct 12 11:49:47 2015 +0300

    libgeda: Replaced separator* procedures with stock guile variants.

