commit 460ab2b2312ce04f88ad82fdf35c12d4b407d071
Author: Edward Hennessy <ehennes@sbcglobal.net>
Date:   Sat Nov 23 12:52:16 2013 -0800

    gschem: Create pan_general and zoom_extents in GschemPageGeometry

