    Closes-bug: lp-908997

commit 5e557fdfcb55b64dea1492df898785694f9ed155
Author: Peter TB Brett <peter@peter-b.co.uk>
Date:   Sat Dec 24 20:07:01 2011 +0000

    scheme-api: Correct bug in set-attribute-value!
    
