commit f5efae4bcb1d79abd21400e08a1bf63bcb43aa4d
Author: Peter Clifton <pcjc2@cam.ac.uk>
Date:   Thu Feb 11 01:34:28 2010 +0000

    gschem: Allow mnemonics for root menus, such as _File, _Edit etc..
    
