commit b7ca06041ea464b0d064bfa965843d2907a83571
Author: Ales Hvezda <ahvezda@seul.org>
Date:   Sun Oct 4 19:39:14 2009 -0400

    Updated the wiki docs from the online version (in prep for the next release)
    
