Date:   Sun Jun 24 23:57:16 2007 -0400

    Removed ancient VOCABULARY file.
    
    This file has been superceeded by the glossary that is in the wiki.

commit 0ed9cf080cfc8509cb29cbe4e976f86b2821c407
